-- MOVES-Cordea Savills appoints Asia director of Institutional Business
-- 
-- Wed Jul 23, 2014 04:54AM EDT
-- None



July 23 (Reuters) - Property investment manager Cordea Savills has appointed Pauline Chong as director of institutional business, South East Asia and Australia.

Chong will spearhead Cordea Savills' development of new business in Malaysia and other regional South East Asian markets, as well as support the company's partners in the region.